{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"13a9089ec2","title":"给王首道的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"467f72a9f3","index":0,"year":1950,"month":6,"day":14,"articleId":"13a9089ec2"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"00fd2f41c1","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"13a9089ec2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王首道（1906-1996），湖南浏阳人。当时任中共湖南省委第一副书记、湖南省人民政府主席。"},{"id":"f1f8282dc5","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"13a9089ec2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周老太太，即周陈轩。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0df15ecd68","type":"title","text":"给王首道的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"13a9089ec2"},{"id":"00fd2f41c1","type":"paragraph","text":"首道同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"13a9089ec2"},{"id":"f1f8282dc5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽草同志的岳母周老太太年已六十，住在湘潭韶山我的家里已有十余年，同当地人民的关系甚好，是一个好老人。她的女儿周文楠同志在沈阳法院工作，现回家去看老太太。老太太前有去东北依其女儿之意，但尚未作决定。如老太太去东北，请你考虑是否可以给以旅费的帮助。如可能，在通例上说得过去的话则帮助之，如不可能，则要她仍住现地不动，请与文楠同志商的办理","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"13a9089ec2"},{"id":"1f21ff5cc7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"13a9089ec2"},{"id":"90fd9c56b3","type":"paragraph","text":"六月十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"13a9089ec2"}],"page":{"id":"0ca58779df","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"13a9089ec2","start":479,"end":479}}}},"__N_SSG":true}